    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "Implementation notes:\n1. List files in Config.inboxFolderId with Google Drive.\n2. For each file, download or OCR text, compute an idempotency key, and write a job JSON matching automation/schemas/finance-job.schema.json into runtimeInboxDir.\n3. Run workerCommand through SSH or Execute Command.\n4. Read the JSON result from runtimeOutputDir.\n5. Append one Documents row for every processed source.\n6. Append a Transactions row for processed or reviewable extraction results.\n7. Append a Review Queue row when review.queue_entry_required is true.\n8. Append a Run Log row with counts for completed, review, failed, and duplicate outcomes.\n9. Move the Drive file to the processed subtype folder, review folder, or error folder without deleting the source.\n\nSee docs/finance-ledger-operating-contract.md for the tab, audit, duplicate, and review lifecycle contract.\n\nThis blueprint is intentionally inactive until repoRoot, folder IDs, and Sheet IDs are configured."
      },
